com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.generic.provider
Class GenericItemProviderAdapterFactory

java.lang.Object
  AdapterFactoryImpl
      com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.generic.util.GenericAdapterFactory
          com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.generic.provider.GenericItemProviderAdapterFactory

public class GenericItemProviderAdapterFactory
extends GenericAdapterFactory

This is the factory that is used to provide the interfaces needed to support Viewers. The adapters generated by this factory convert EMF adapter notifications into calls to fireNotifyChanged. The adapters also support Eclipse property sheets. Note that most of the adapters are shared among multiple instances.
